desc_long								关于这款游戏							In Sword 'N' Board, you play as Sidd a young kid going on a pretend adventure in his backyard in search of his missing video game console! You'll fight through imaginary monsters, find secrets and solve puzzles using the items you find on your adventure. Each of your items can be combined with other items in your inventory to enhance their uses! All of your items and their item combinations will be able to be used to fight monsters and solve puzzles during your adventure! As you find more and more items and unlock additional item combinations the puzzles will only become more complicated and difficult!Blacksmith to craft forged items and upgrade stats!Unique item combinations.Unique blend of hand drawn assets and pixel art!Multiple save slotsA constantly growing Overworld to exploreHard to find secrets! (No hand holding here!)						
